name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.connection-keep-alive.timeout
description:
The number of seconds a shuffle client attempts to retain
   http connection. Refer "Keep-Alive: timeout=" header in
   Http specification

name: dfs.block.access.key.update.interval
description: Interval in minutes at which namenode updates its access keys.

name: dfs.client.deadnode.detection.probe.suspectnode.interval.ms
description: Interval time in milliseconds for probing suspect node behavior.

name: dfs.client.retry.max.attempts
description: Max retry attempts for DFSClient talking to namenodes.

name: dfs.namenode.top.window.num.buckets
description: Number of buckets in the rolling window implementation of nntop
